Description: WOW! Gibson ES-339 Memphis Custom 2016 Sunset Burst + OHSC and COA Lovies guitars is offering up an unplayed ES-339 in a beautiful Sunset Burst! The ES-339 is the close cousin the the ES-335 on a smaller body version. This allows it to be played with more comfort whether you’re sitting or standing. These guitars have great rich and versatile tones, you could play anything from country to pop to hard rock! SEE many HD images below! This guitar is very clean, it has some light scratches near the pickguard and maybe a couple of little surface markings.kmn WEIGHS in at 6.90 .882″ at the 1st fret .953″ at the 12th fret 1.688″ Nut Width Serial: 12856725 SKU: 1899 The ES-339 became an instant modern classic by “compacting” the iconic ES-335 body shape in a lighter, more comfortably-playing guitar, and the new 2016 rendition from Gibson Memphis is better than ever. Body: Classic ES-335 shape redrawn to smaller dimensions Fingerboard: Rosewood with small block inlays Neck: Redesigned dimensions for improved strength and playabilty Truss rod: Historic truss rod Pickups: Burstbucker 1 & 2 Bridge: ABR-1 with titanium saddles Tailpiece: Locking stopbar Finish: High-gloss nitrocellulose lacquer _gsrx_vers_841 (GS 7.0.16 (841))
